message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. This product is worth more than $120 to me, but I believe in making it accessible to those who appreciate its true worth. I am offering it to you for $150. It comes with a satisfaction guarantee, and if you're not completely satisfied, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund. Let's make this deal happen!
